Version:	0.95a
Release:	1
Group:		Applications/Sound
License:	GPL
Source0:	http://rucus.ru.ac.za/~urban/projects/playmp3list/download/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
# Source0-md5:	542640950fe05519f2e77a9e6f99438a
